{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_11_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 莉央のお世話で大変だ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……あ、葵！　良かった、やっと見つけた\n随分探したんだからな……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… Ah‚ Aoi! Thank goodness‚ I finally found you.\nI’ve been looking everywhere for you… haa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.9541040738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、{user}君？　どうしたのさ\nそんなに息切れして、運動不足なんじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ {user}-kun? What’s wrong?\nYou’re that out of breath—aren’t you out of shape?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1487725413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、葵よりは運動不足かもしれないけど……\n……じゃなくて、葵を呼びに来たんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I might be more out of shape than you…\n…But that’s not the point. I came to get you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "撮影中にふらっといなくなって慌ててたら\n莉央さんが、この公園にいるかもって教えてくれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you suddenly disappeared during the shoot‚ we panicked\nand Rio-san said you might be in this park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.380997308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、いきなり機材トラブルだって言うしさ\n復旧するまで、ただ待ってるのも暇だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ they suddenly said there was equipment trouble.\nJust waiting around until it’s fixed is boring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5047160465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "で、近くに公園があったのを思い出して\n久々にここで踊るのも悪くないかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I remembered there’s a park nearby.\nI thought dancing here again after so long wouldn’t be bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5047160465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9732648212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵らしいな……でも、故障はなんとかなったらしい\n撮影も再開するから、ロケ場所に戻ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s so like you… but it seems the malfunction’s been fixed.\nFilming’s starting again‚ so let’s head back to the location.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.0512012162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、もう少し休憩時間延びない？\nこんな短い時間じゃ、踊った気がしないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ can’t the break be a little longer?\nWith such a short time‚ it doesn’t even feel like I danced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影が終わったらいくらでも踊れるだろ？\nそれに、今日はそうもいかないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can dance all you want after the shoot‚ right?\nBesides‚ today’s not that kind of day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.9873004275
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "『LizNoir・BIG4までの軌跡』の撮影なんだ\n初期メンバーの葵がいないと始まらない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the shoot for “LizNoir: The Path to the BIG4.”\nIt can’t start without you‚ one of the original members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……分かったよ。莉央にガミガミ言われたくないし\nこころと愛の前で、僕があんまりルーズなのもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… alright. I don’t want Rio nagging me anyway.\nAnd I don’t want to look too sloppy in front of Kokoro and Ai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.248570442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、莉央さんもよくこの公園が分かったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ Rio-san knew this park surprisingly well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.731449731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.731449731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ここからバンプロのオフィスは近いからね\nデビューした頃は、よくここで気晴らしに踊ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Van Pro’s office is close to here.\nBack when we debuted‚ I used to come here to dance and clear my head.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7019488969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.8605652491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央は、最初の頃は知らなかったんだけどね\n昔、大喧嘩した時に、この公園を知られちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio didn’t know about it at first‚ though.\nBut during a huge fight a long time ago‚ she found out about this park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3686155635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕が踊ってたら、すぐ連れ戻しに来るようになったんだ\nまったく、酷いと思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ whenever I danced here‚ she’d come drag me back.\nSeriously‚ don’t you think that’s cruel?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4686155635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも昔から苦労してたんだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san’s had a hard time for a long while‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7109277407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0784106731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　苦労っていうのは、どういう意味？\nまるで僕が悪いみたいだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What do you mean by “had a hard time”?\nThat makes it sound like it was my fault.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5070281186,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3059.638548099997,
          "startTime": 120.5666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5859.638548099994,
          "startTime": 123.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そういう訳じゃ……あ、スタジオから連絡だ\n十五分後に撮影再開らしい、急いで戻ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ that’s not what I meant… Oh‚ message from the studio.\nFilming resumes in fifteen minutes—let’s hurry back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.9381618976
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.9381618976
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 130.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……お、まだ機材のチェック中みたいだ\nこれなら、ギリギリ遅刻せずにすんだかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ looks like they’re still checking the equipment.\nGuess we barely made it without being late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7512922444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遅れちゃいないが、みんな葵を心配してたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re not late‚ but everyone was worried about you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7748963196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まったく、撮影の時まで踊りに行くなんてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ going off to dance even during a shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5512922444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.0265063444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんじゃないか、めずらしい\nいつも会議会議で、現場に来る暇なんかなさそうなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Saegusa-san. That’s rare.\nYou’re always stuck in meetings‚ so I figured you’d have no time to come here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6512922444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "リズノワ結成当時の話もするって言うなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they’re talking about the early days of LizNoir",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.832379357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "俺だって、時間くらい作るさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can make time too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2263809601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.0352592308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
